</local:MyCard><local:MyCard Title="重磅更新！！！服务器现在有更多食物了！！！" CanSwap="True" IsSwaped="False" Style="{StaticResource Card}" >
<StackPanel Style="{StaticResource ContentStack}">
<FlowDocumentScrollViewer >
<FlowDocument>
<Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H1}">重磅更新！！！服务器现在有更多食物了！！！</Paragraph><Paragraph>发布时间: 2024-08-20 14:55:58</Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/132807-boen_shi-66c499e7e43a6.jpeg"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph>没错，你没听错，原版现在有更多食物了！</Paragraph><Paragraph><Bold>现腐竹制作了 4 种自定义作物，70+种自定义食物！</Bold><Span TextDecorations="Strikethrough">（创意借鉴农夫乐事 mod）</Span></Paragraph><Paragraph><InlineUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/141414-boen_shi-66c4a4b6a345e.jpeg"/></InlineUIContainer><InlineUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/141559-boen_shi-66c4a51f0f58f.webp"/></InlineUIContainer><InlineUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/141418-boen_shi-66c4a4ba82b56.jpeg"/></InlineUIContainer><InlineUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/141421-boen_shi-66c4a4bda941e.jpeg"/></InlineUIContainer><InlineUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/141454-boen_shi-66c4a4de3a166.jpeg"/></InlineUIContainer></Paragraph><Paragraph>而且，这个食物的图标、显示名称、恢复饱食度和饱和度都是自定义的。</Paragraph><Paragraph><Bold>不会玩？不可能的。服务器配有配方书，方便玩家游玩。</Bold></Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/133302-boen_shi-66c49b0e32d4d.webp"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph><Bold>基岩版呢？当然也可以！</Bold></Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/133427-boen_shi-66c49b63242ca.jpeg"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph><Bold>好了，废话少说，现在开始游玩教程：</Bold></Paragraph><Paragraph>首先，无论 Java 版和基岩版进入游戏，请同意资源包。</Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/133833-boen_shi-66c49c591277d.jpeg"/></BlockUIContainer><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/133933-boen_shi-66c49c952be1e.webp"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph>服务器添加了 4 种自定义食物：</Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/134638-boen_shi-66c49e3ebe48b.webp"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}"><Bold>作物获取</Bold></Paragraph><Paragraph>1、 野外会自然生成 （如上图）</Paragraph><Paragraph>2、 通过打草获得其种子 （12.5% 概率），通过农田种植获得</Paragraph><Paragraph>种植后，获得 4 种作物：卷心菜、洋葱、稻穗、番茄</Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/134403-boen_shi-66c49da3a62e8.webp"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph>服务器所有的配方都可以在 「配方书」 中找到。</Paragraph><Paragraph>配方书配方：</Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/134908-boen_shi-66c49ed4bc8e5.webp"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph>有几种制作食物的工具：普通工作台、普通炉灶 （熔炉、烟熏炉）、菜板、锅 （配合灶台使用）</Paragraph><Paragraph>不同制作事物的工具的配方有不同的分类，详细请见配方书。</Paragraph><Paragraph>普通工作台和普通炉灶就不多讲了，和原版使用的方法一致。</Paragraph><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}"><Bold>菜板</Bold></Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/135451-boen_shi-66c4a02b782fe.jpeg"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph>配方在配方书中有，可自行查询</Paragraph><Paragraph>放下来是一个压力板</Paragraph><Paragraph>如何使用？</Paragraph><Paragraph>先查询配方，查看可以进行的操作</Paragraph><Paragraph>再制作一把刀，配方书理由配方。</Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/135624-boen_shi-66c4a088ccc30.webp"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph><Bold>Java 版：左手拿着需要切割物品，右手拿着刀，对准菜板右键切割即可获得</Bold></Paragraph><Paragraph><Bold>基岩版：右手拿着物品单击菜板，在 5s 之内拿着刀再单击菜板切割即可获得</Bold></Paragraph><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}"><Bold>锅 （配合灶台使用）</Bold></Paragraph><Paragraph>请先制作锅和炉灶，配方在配方书</Paragraph><Paragraph>按如下方法摆放：</Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/140337-boen_shi-66c4a239e21a5.webp"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph><Bold>上方是锅，下方是炉灶</Bold></Paragraph><Paragraph>打开炉灶，放入煤，并点击 「篝火」，即可点火</Paragraph><BlockUIContainer><local:MyImage Style="{StaticResource InnerImage}" Source="https://mc.boen.fun/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/140553-boen_shi-66c4a2c1d0599.webp"/></BlockUIContainer><Paragraph>这时，打开锅 （其实就是工作台界面），按照配方书中的配发制作即可！</Paragraph><Paragraph>总而言之，多看配方书，没问题哦！</Paragraph><Paragraph>如果遇到 BUG，请马上 @腐竹，感谢！</Paragraph><Paragraph>祝大家玩得开心！<Span TextDecorations="Strikethrough">（后期可能有 DLC 哦！）</Span></Paragraph><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}"><Bold>这就是食物拓展的玩法，大家快来玩吧！</Bold></Paragraph>
